The Angelina Malfitano Conference Room is on the Third Floor of the Memorial Union, and serves as ASUCD ASUCDs conference room.  The room is named in honor of the former chair of GASC, Angelina Malfitano.  The room was dedicated in her honor in a ceremony on June 4, 2009.

On the wall, there is a large plaque bearing the name of allASUCD President  of the past ASUCD Presidents.  It serves as a shrine to the history of student governance at UCD, as well as a small but functional conference room.
